        <div class="glass rounded-xl p-6 mb-4">
          <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-faint)] mb-2">Extended NISS v2.0 Vector (with neurological weighting)</p>
          <p class="font-[family-name:var(--font-mono)] text-xs text-[var(--color-accent-tertiary)] break-all">
            NISS:2.0/BI:H/CR:H/CD:M/CV:E/RV:P/NP:T/R:0.7/FI:0.8/PS:0.6/CE:0.5/MC:0.9
